The ultimate locations of these files are:

dhcpd.conf - /etc/dhcp/dhcpd.conf
hostapd.conf - /etc/hostapd/hostapd.conf
interfaces[.aphost][.apclient] - /etc/network/interfaces
isc-dhcp-server[.aphost][.apclient] - /etc/default/isc-dhcp-server
rc.local[.aphost][.apclient] - /etc/rc.local

*.aphost denotes files used when in configuration mode

All files used in configuration mode:

dhcpd.conf
hostapd.conf
interfaces.aphost
isc-dhcp-server.aphost
rc.local.aphost



*.apclient denotes files used when in regular use mode

All files used in configuration mode:

interfaces.apclient
isc-dhcp-server.apclient
rc.local.apclient
